{"tid":330573,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★ios 10.3.3出現大量明顯的 Bug！","createTime":"2017-07-21T10:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T21:05:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f3a86ec9a5ff28861884c3c172273eaebbe667","tid":330573,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"根據國外用戶反映，iOS 10.3.3 中存在一個明顯的 Bug：用戶無法清除 Safari 流覽器中的歷史記錄和網站數據。該問題已經連續出現在 iOS 10 的 4 個版本中，蘋果支持社區收到數百個有關此問題的反饋。<br />\n<br />\n　　威鋒網友在升級 iOS 10.3.3 後也向我們反映了部分問題，首先談論最多的要數橫屏 Bug。橫屏 Bug 的表現為用戶在 iPhone 控制中心啟動&ldquo;豎排方向鎖定&rdquo;，然後開啟橫屏遊戲或應用，之後雙擊 Home 鍵，設備會出現卡屏問題。鋒友表示，iOS 10.0 發布以來就存在橫屏 Bug，iOS 10.3.3 顯然也沒修復這一問題。<br />\n<br />\n　　還有少數鋒友反映，在使用 iOS 10.3.3 過程中，出現設備鎖屏後 Wi-Fi 斷連，iPhone 播放音樂時音量會自動變小以及備忘錄、提醒事項應用出現閃退的問題。不知道升級了 iOS 10.3.3 的你有沒出現同樣的狀況？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.feng.com/iPhone/news/2017-07-21/IOS-10.3.3-Bug-but-still-worth-the-upgrade_686068.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.feng.com%2FiPhone%2Fnews%2F2017-07-21%2FIOS-10.3.3-Bug-but-still-worth-the-upgrade_686068.shtml&d=lQxHVXYVGApsbYdR3oXkxrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=63c88097\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.feng.com/iPhone/news/2017-07-21/IOS-10.3.3-Bug-but-still-worth-the-upgrade_686068.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"9386117e75e145ab5913ef53b0c9da13d182a776","tid":330573,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627c3d2a4b34d0180cc1b86450ba5837a221ffdc","tid":330573,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:43:42.000Z","msg":"1 用戶無法清除 Safari 流覽器中的歷史記錄和網站數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2 橫屏 Bug 的表現為用戶在 iPhone 控制中心啟動&ldquo;豎排方向鎖定&rdquo;，然後開啟橫屏遊戲或應用，之後雙擊 Home 鍵，設備會出現卡屏問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3 設備鎖屏後 Wi-Fi 斷連，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4 iPhone 播放音樂時音量會自動變小<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5 備忘錄、提醒事項應用出現閃退的問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9ffeacd02d207d694a9be702b7341b4f95860f","tid":330573,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05023e34ffcb066f4f3ad9af3d25363219c1b5c0","tid":330573,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfd93ffd14f44b9c83b1b8e3c6b2716bbee6ad0","tid":330573,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人block哂"},{"pid":"836a69d08fbcb016dab3f395bcd47ca3773c7e5a","tid":330573,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"6. 個Safari冇用一陣，會自動同我將本身開咗嘅分頁全部閂哂，得返一版blank page"},{"pid":"5e2f09f6df0333da34e5ea1c20a452cb424e9e0c","tid":330573,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,